text: Novomeshcherovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Novomeshcherovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 526 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Novomeshcherovo
